gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 133, Lakers 110
gameRecap.excerpt: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander led the Thunder with 33 points, seven assists, and four rebounds as Oklahoma City defeated the Lakers, 133-110. Jalen Williams added 21 points and seven assists as Chet Holmgren totaled 18 points and five rebounds in the win. Anthony Davis (31 points, 14 rebounds) and LeBron James (21 points, 12 rebounds, six assists) led the Lakers. The Thunder improve to 12-6 on the year as the Lakers move to 11-9.
